# ScholarHub HPU Site Map

This sitemap documents all publicly accessible modules, pages, and entry points of the ScholarHub platform across the Gateway and the respective sub-portals (ScholarSync and ScholarTrack).

---

## 1. Main Gateway
* **Base URL**: `https://scholarhubhpu.in`
* **Route Layout**:
  * [Landing / Portal Selector Page](https://scholarhubhpu.in/) (`/`) - Central gateway allowing users to route to either ScholarSync (academic lifecycle tracking) or ScholarTrack (daily attendance/leave management).

---

